title: Clint Eastwood premieres his latest film 'The 15:17 to Paris' in LA
text:
Clint Eastwood premieres his latest film 'The 15:17 to Paris' in LA 8:31am EST - 01:19 
Hollywood Legend Eastwood attends 'The 15:17 to Paris' world premiere, featuring for the first time three non-actors as themselves in a thriller based on real-life events.
